OL,3,CCardiff University 'actively
OL,4,Creviewing' Huw Edwards' honours after
OL,5,Cguilty plea
OL,7,FA Cardiff University spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "In light of a guilty plea,
OL,9,FCardiff University is actively
OL,10,Freviewing procedures in relation to
OL,11,Fthe honorary fellowship award and his
OL,12,Fposition as an honorary professor. We
OL,13,Fhave no further comment on the matter."
OL,15,FIn 2003, Edwards was made an honorary
OL,16,Ffellow of the University of Wales and
OL,17,Fin 2007 he became an honorary
OL,18,Fprofessor of Journalism at Cardiff
OL,19,FUniversity.
