OL,7,FHis profile on Cardiff University's
OL,8,F'People' page has been taken down.
OL,10,FToday, Westminster Magistrates' Court
OL,11,Fheard the 62-year-old had been
OL,12,Finvolved in online chat with an adult
OL,13,Fman on WhatsApp between December 2020
OL,14,Fand August 2021, who sent him 377
OL,15,Fsexual images, of which 41 were
OL,16,Findecent images of children.
OL,18,FThe bulk of these, 36, were sent
OL,19,Fduring a two-month period.
